+                      ></small
+                    >
+                  </p>
+                  <div class="pf-v6-c-content">
+                    <p>
+                      <small
+                        >Our <a href="#conduct">Code of Conduct</a> applies in
+                        all VanLUG spaces.</small
+                      >
+                    </p>
+                  </div>
+                </div>
+                <div class="pf-v6-l-grid__item pf-m-12-col pf-m-6-col-on-md">
+                  <div class="pf-v6-c-content">
+                    <p>
+                      <small
+                        >VanLUG is a registered non-profit organization with the
+                        <a
+                          href="https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/employment-business/business/not-for-profit-organizations"
+                          target="_blank"
+                          rel="noreferrer noopener"
+                          >BC Provincial Government</a
+                        >. Run entirely by volunteers, we've been bringing Linux
+                        and open-source enthusiasts together in Vancouver since
